programme.desc: The notorious outlaw, Jud Starr, is rescued from hanging by his old gang. Against her will, Jud takes his former sweetheart, an Indian girl, back to her tribe.

programme.title: Stormcast Westerns Movies - The Gun and The Pulpit
programme.desc: A gunfighter masquerades as a preacher to hide his identity from the posse who is pursuing him. He ends up ridding his new town of the menace of a tyrannical local rancher.

programme.title: Hawkeye and the Last of the Mohicans
programme.sub-title: S01 : E10 Hawkeye and the Last of the Mohicans - The Servant
programme.desc: Hawkeye and Chingachgook find a runaway Irish girl wandering alone in the forest. They learn that she is an indentured servant who was sold into slavery.

programme.title: Stormcast Westerns Movies - Mohawk
programme.desc: A Boston artist (Scott Brady) goes west to paint authentic Western themes in the 1700s. He juggles his fiance and a variety of fetching models until war breaks out with the Indians and he is caught in the middle.

programme.title: Hawkeye and the Last of the Mohicans
programme.sub-title: S01 : E11 Hawkeye and the Last of the Mohicans - The Search
programme.desc: When Hawkeye and Chingachgook save a woman from two Indians trying to kidnap her, she asks them to help find her son who was taken in an Indian attack 18 years before.

programme.title: Stormcast Westerns Movies - Santa Fe Trail
programme.desc: A group of West Point graduates are assigned to the U.S. Cavalry in Kansas during the time of abolitionist John Brown. Stars Ronald Reagan.

programme.title: Cimarron Strip
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Cimarron Strip - Broken Wing
programme.desc: When a parson is shot, a rancher’s son is arrested. After the preacher recovers and won’t press charges, a saloon owner and his armed sidekick rally the town to take justice into their own hands.

programme.title: Stormcast Westerns Movies - Mclintock
programme.desc: Cattle baron George Washington McLintock battles his headstrong wife (Maureen OHara), a ranch hand (Patrick Wayne) who wants to marry his daughter (Stefanie Powers) and evil-doers in this upbeat comedy Western with a memorable ending.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E11 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 11, Romania
programme.desc: Situated in the very heart of the Carpathian Mountains, Sibiu is a Romanian town where the climate is pleasantly mild, offering some of the best weather conditions for a strongman event around Europe. All this, without doubt, set the mood for the high results and showtime vibes in Stage 11 of Strongman Champions League. The competition in Sibiu was organized in six different disciplines

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E12 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 12, Curacao
programme.desc: From now on every stage of these series will be more than crucial. Curacao is a beautiful Dutch island in the Caribbean, with a great atmosphere to hold another stage of the MLO Strongman Champions League. Let’s see who takes the title here and who will secure a place in the next stage.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E13 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 13, Jordan
programme.desc: Ten of the world’s strongest men gathered in Amman to compete in Jordan’s first-ever Truck-Pull Championship. The contestants race against the clock while pulling a 21-ton truck across the track. One of the most fierce competitors to take part in the event was four-time winner of the World’s Strongest Man competition, Brian Shaw.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E14 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 14, Greece
programme.desc: Taking place in Corinth, Greece, considered by many the cradle of the sports competition games, an epic strongman battle will mark the last stage before the upcoming big two-day season’s finale in Chetumal, Mexico. In front of more than 5000 spectators, the twelve athletes compete in Log Lifts, Card Deadlift, Conan’s Wheel and Loading.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E15 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 15, Mexico World Finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: The first day of the two-part finale sees the strongest men competing in Carry and Drag, Dumbbell Lift and the Truck Pull. Everything is possible in this heated fight for the crown against the backdrop of stunning Chetumal, Mexico.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S04 : E16 SCL 2017 Season 4, Episode 16, Mexico World Finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: On the second day of the grand finale of the 2017 Strongman Champions League, the athletes have a last chance to secure the medals in the spectacular four events Weight for Height, Deadlift Cars, Forward Hold and The Loading Medley. Be prepared for stunning performances – and even world records!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E01 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 1, Norway - World Strongest Viking
programme.desc: Season 2018 begins with 14 strongest men in the world, all competing for the title. The competition kicks off in Norway. We’ll see typical Viking disciplines, team events and world records in heavy conditions in the land of snow and ice. They will suffer, they will freeze and fight in this first competition of the year for the title that they will carry on their shoulders throughout whole year.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E02 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 2, Germany - FIBO Power
programme.desc: The next stop in strongest league of the world is muscle capital, largest number of strong shoulders per capichampions league on the planet. It’s a FIBO - the biggest expo on planet Earth and the second stage of 2018 Strongman champions league, in Cologne, Germany.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E03 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 3, Abu Dhabi
programme.desc: For the first time in history, Strongman Champions League will set up competition in Abu Dhabi. The line-up of super athletes, who are part of the SCL, includes former world champions Dainis Zageris (Latvia) and Krzysztof Radzikowski (Poland), current world champion Matjaz Belsak (Slovenia) and biggest strongman in the World Sean O’Hagan (Ireland).

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E04 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 4, Holland (Part 1)
programme.desc: Strongman classic in land where there is no place for anything else excepts strength, fight and endurance. Here are fourteen of the strongest men, fighting for the title of strongest in Holland.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E05 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 5, Holland (Part 2)
programme.desc: We go back to Holland, where former champion Dainis Zageris is in leading position after the first three events. Alongside Radzikowski, he is in this moment favorite for world title, and also leader shirt holder.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E06 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 6, Finland
programme.desc: Stage six of Strongman champions league, 2018 is set back on north, in Finland. Here we have Matjaz Belsak, wearing SCL leader shirt, one of the biggest strongman in the World Mika Torro, fan favorite strongman in all over the World – Will Baggott, and also big name from Baltic – Aivars Smaukstelis

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E07 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 7, Serbia
programme.desc: Twelve strongman, including defending Worldchampion Matjaz Belsak from Slovenia , will compete on “Air spa” for the title of best in homeland country of Tesla, Pupin, Novak Djokovic. Matjaz Belsak is the SCL leader in this competition, chasing his third victory this season.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E08 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 8, Finland - U105 (Part 1)
programme.desc: The World championship in lightweights of the Strongman Champions League bring to us 50 strongmen from all over the world. All athletes are under 105 kilograms and for them this is the step up to the ultimate heavyweights.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E09 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 9, Finland - U105 (Part 2)
programme.desc: In this second stage of the World championship of lightweights we will find out who out of the 12 athletes will win the title in the under 105 kilogram category.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E10 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 10, Romania (Part 1)
programme.desc: The first part of SCL Romania 2018 will be hosted in Brasov. This episode features a new event for Strongman Champion League: “ The Chopper Pull”!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E11 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 11, Romania (Part 2)
programme.desc: After three classical Strongman events – Dead lift, Loading and Front hold – and one historical, Chopper Pull for the first time in history of Strongman, now we go to find out who will take title in Romania. This is the second stage in Romania and it remains to be seen who will win the title; Aivars, Travis or Krzyzstof?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E12 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 12, Curacao (Part 1)
programme.desc: The next destination of Strongman Champions League is in a piece of paradise on earth – Curacao. We bring to you some special Strongman events like the Rock Lift, Tug of War and Weight for Height in this episode.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E13 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 13, Curacao (Part 2)
programme.desc: This is the last competition before the grand finals. After the first three events Zageris is in top place, but can O’Hagan, Baggott, Petursson and Ortmayer step into the final? Last chance some of them will find through events like Forward Hold, Truck Pull, Dead Lift and loading very big objects.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E14 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 14, Road to Mexico
programme.desc: We bring you 50 minutes of Strongman inside. Fears, inspiration, courage, the best and worst from our finalists and their expectation of the finals. We also go to Poland and Germany to represent one day in the training of Krzysztof Radzikowski and Dennis Kohlruss. See all the finalists for Mexico in their comfort zone here, with their backgrounds /motivations /family and friends.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E15 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 15, Mexico - World Finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: The first part of the Strongman Champions League 2018 finals in Mexico. The last twelve athletes all pushing their boundaries and testing their limits to take the World title.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S05 : E16 SCL 2018 Season 5, Episode 16, Mexico - World Finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: After 11 months and 14 competitions all over the world, it all comes down to the final in this episode. The strongmen must show their best skills and every mistake is expensive, so their concentration must be at the highest possible level. Will Krzysztof manage to take off back or will Dainis maintain his lead?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E01 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 1, World Strongest Viking
programme.desc: This year 14 athletes from all over the world came to Fefor to compete in 6 cruel events. Well see typical Viking disciplines on very heavy conditions in land of snow and ice, World records and athletes like the title defender Krzysztof Radzikowski, strongest guys from Holland and Germany and many more

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E02 SCL S6 Ep2 FIBO Power
programme.desc: The next stop in strongest league of the world is muscle capital, largest number of strong shoulders per capita in the World and of course, the most powerful host in Strongman champions league on the planet. It’s a FIBO - the biggest expo on planet Earth and the second stage of 2019 Strongman champions league, in Cologne, Germany.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E03 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 3, Turkey
programme.desc: On a spectacular beach in Alanya, the MLO Strongman Champions League Turkey was viewed by thousands of spectators over a two day battle. With 12 athletes at the start over 6 cruel events, like Marble Stone Lift, Truckpull and Deadlift cars. And with the comeback of Travis Ortmayer / USA, former stone king and world ranked competitor. Winner of several SCL stages in the past.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E04 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 4, Holland (Part 1)
programme.desc: Four times Strongest Man of Holland, Alex Moonen and the “Flying Dutchman” Kelvin de Ruiter competing here in Holland against 12 other strongest men in the world. There were 6 events in total, and 3 in this episode: The first event, a truckpull of 17.000 kg over 25 meters in max 75 seconds, was a real hard pull Also for the World Champion Truckpull, Holland’s runner-up Kelvin de Ruiter, but watch his amazing technique here.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E05 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 5, Holland (Part 2)
programme.desc: Strongest Man of Holland, Alex Moonen and the “Flying Dutchman” Kelvin de Ruiter, competing in Holland against 12 other strongest men in the world. There were 6 events in total, 3 in this second episode; a Viking-press of 150 kg with the current world record holder Luke Herrick. The fifth event, a front hold of 25 kg is loved or hated by the athletes and lastly, the Stones of Strength.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E06 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 6, Russia
programme.desc: An unbelievable TANK PULL of 50.000 kg was at the stage of SCL RUSSIA. Never seen this before! Not only a tank pull was done here but also the Viking Press/ Deadlift Max and Log lift reps were spectacular events to see here in Russia. With Mikhail Koklyaev also as event presenter, the former top 3 world strongest man from Russia was there

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E07 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 7, Serbia
programme.desc: In this year’s edition on The Balkan Peninsula, we have competing the new talent from Estonia Marko Remlik together with Sebastian Kurek from Poland and yellow leader Kelvin de Ruiter

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E08 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 8, Finland (Part 1)
programme.desc: Mateusz Kieliszkowski from Poland and Aivars Smaukstelis from Latvia are the strongman future of these days. Mateusz is the best man in the World at the moment to defeat. Only 25 years and such a fantastic strongman. They come here only for a win. But there are 12 more Strong athletes in this episode who want the title of Finland as well.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E09 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 9, Finland (Part 2)
programme.desc: Mateusz Is leading after day 1 (previous episode) with close behind him Aivars Smaukstelis and Zake Muluzi from the UK. All very exciting! 5 events in this episode: Log Lift, Fram Walk, Deadlift, Sack Throw (Weight for Height), Loading medley.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E10 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 10, Portugal
programme.desc: In this stage we have a new strong debutant: Oleg Sylka from the Ukraine. He is the new talent, who will stand up against the old champions like ZSydrunas Savickas and Brian Shaw and the Stoltman Brother from the UK. This new talent Oleg is a great character and we will see him flame in the episode in Portugal.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E11 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 11, Callio
programme.desc: In Callio is the deepest mine of Europe/ 1500 meter deep, whereas the MLO Strongman Champions League also did 1 event. The Forward Hold, on a 1500 dept/ also a kind of new record/ as it was never done before. Spectacular and new in Strongman sport.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E12 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 12, Ukraine
programme.desc: Kelvin de Ruiter is here to defend his SCL World Truck Pull Championships title. But this year, another strong field wants his title. Over 3 different pulls with 3 different trucks, and 14 athletes at the start, it will be difficult for everybody.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E13 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 13, Caribbean
programme.desc: SCL edition Curacao 2019 was a great event, twelve power boys from all over made a great show at the white beaches, and 35 degrees Celsius heat in the Carrabean Islands. Two events were held on Friday at the beach of beautiful resort Sunscape, the other three were held near the world famous floating bridge at Willemstad on Saturday night.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E14 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 14, Dubai
programme.desc: Hosted at Meydan Grandstand in Dubai, the Strongman Champions League had some really big names in the list like Mateusz Kieliszkowski from Poland, Brian Shaw from the USA and Krzysztof Radzikowski. In front of the Burj Khalifa the athletes do the deadlift max and 4 other heavy events at another spot in Dubai.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E15 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 15, World Finals (Part 1)
programme.desc: With new places on the calendar, over 16 stages, broadcasting in over 100 countries and in its 13th year, the MLO Strongman Champions League (SCL) can be seen truly as the biggest strongman league in the world. The last stage over 2 episodes of the MLO Strongman Champions League, were held in Porto, Portugal. This competition in Portugal is full of memorable performances and strong results.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S06 : E16 SCL 2019 Season 6, Episode 16, World Finals (Part 2)
programme.desc: With new places on the calendar, over 16 stages, broadcasting in over 100 countries and in its 13th year, the MLO Strongman Champions League (SCL) can be seen truly as the biggest strongman league in the world. This competition in Portugal is full of memorable performances and strong results and this is the final!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E01 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 1, Norway
programme.desc: The spectacular Fefor Arena hosted for the 8th time the Worlds Strongest Viking, part of the SCL World Series. But with the absence of former title holders its anyones game. Again, a very spectacular episode of the Strongman Champions League here in Norway.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E02 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 2, Finland (Part 1)
programme.desc: In this episode, the Titan, former double World champion from Latvia will compete against his fellow countryman and the current World champion - Aivars Smaukstelis. With 8 events over 2 stages the contestants are pushed to their limits in Finland.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E03 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 3, Finland (Part 2)
programme.desc: Dainis Zageris and Aivars Smaukstelis, both from Latvia have a serious, strong battle in the this second and final episode of the SCL Finland 2020. Watch the unbelievable and brute power of these athletes in the last 4 events to crown the winner.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E04 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 4, World Record Breakers
programme.desc: The SCL Germany event takes place in an ancient castle called Die Burg in the heart of Germany. Its here where 5 world record attempts take place across 5 different events with 10 athletes. They will go to the max! See this and much more in the SCL Germany 2020.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E05 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 5, Strongest Viking
programme.desc: SCL Norway is normally all about snow, wind, and cold weather. Our brave athletes are used to compete under conditions few other athletes have competed in, but after COVID delays the competition has been moved from winter to summer bringing in a whole new range of challenges. With an impressive athlete list who will be the winner across 5 cruel events?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E06 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 6, World Strongest Team 1
programme.desc: Were in sunny Finland for the next stage of a double-bill of SCL action, but this time its a team event. A truly fantastic event with 6000 spectators. Even during COVID times this was exceptional! 8 Strong Teams where fighting for the title over a crazy 9 events.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E07 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 7, World Strongest Team 2
programme.desc: Day 2 of the famous Team World championship here in Finland, done over 9 cruel events. In this episode the last and final 5 events take place. 8 Strong Teams are fighting for the title.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E08 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 8, Portugal
programme.desc: The next set of challenges are set in sunny Esposende in Portugal. With stars such as Travis Ortmayer, Kelvin de Ruiter from Holland, and Ervin Toots from Estonia. While Fabio Silva will defend the honour in his own country.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E09 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 9, World Records (Part 1)
programme.desc: We are back in Germany, with the world record breakers. We promise you this is going to be amazing. Do not move from that seat, because we are going to see some records smashed today. Over 6 cruel events, you will see who gets crowned of the King Of The Castle!

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E10 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 10, World Records (Part 2)
programme.desc: With the next episode of Strongman Champions League Germany. Its the world record breakers, and in the last show we set two new records. Can more be records be broken before the king of the castle is crowned?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E11 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 11, Worlds 105 Kg (Part 1)
programme.desc: Welcome to Kokkola in Finland. This city will be the setting for the Lightweight World championship. Out of 24 athletes, only 16 will make it through to the final day, but who will champion each event and who is going to be eliminated?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E12 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 12, Worlds 105 Kg (Part 2)
programme.desc: Its the second day, and the top 16 athletes have made it through to the final round. With another 4 events to go who will get the crown of world champion?

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E13 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 13, Ukraine
programme.desc: Welcome to Ukraine and the wonderful capital city of Kyiv. Were here for the second time for the iconic truck pull World Championships! The reigning World champion Kelvin de Ruiter from Holland will defend his title.

programme.title: Strongman Champions League
programme.sub-title: S07 : E14 SCL 2021 Season 7, Episode 14, Romania
programme.desc: In this episode, a final chance for our athletes to get vital world series ranking points on board to give them the best possible chance of success and an initial advantage at the finals. Its the last show before the world finals and the top 10 places are up for grabs, but who will they be?

programme.title: The Condemned 2
programme.desc: Palkkatappaja Will Tanner epaonnistuu yrityksessaan napata vaarallisen uhkapeliringin johtaja, minka jalkeen han saakin itse viholliset peraansa. Tassa pelissa on vain elavia maaleja ja haviaja menettaa henkensa.

programme.title: Meidan gangstereiden kesken
programme.desc: Painija Charlie ja jaatelonmyyja Sonny ovat huolettomia ja mukavia kavereita, jotka pysyttelevat poissa vaikeuksista. Mutta kun kaupungin ja alamaailman johtaja erehtyy luulemaan heita pahamaineiseksi tappajakaksikoksi, kaikki muuttuu... Pelastaakseen omat nahkansa Charlie ja Sonny pysyvat vaiti todellisista henkilollisyyksistaan ja pelaavat mukana hamatakseen gangstereita. Kun Charlie ja Tom saavat tehtavakseen hoidella kilpaileva perhe paivilta, ei heille jaa muuta mahdollisuutta kuin ottaa ohjat omiin kasiinsa... Bud Spencerin ystavaa Sonnya nayttelee Giuliano Gemma. Han on muun muassa vaikuttanut spaghettiwesternelokuvassa ”Ringo - tappaja” ja Dario Argenton jannarissa ”Tenebre”.

programme.title: Raining in the Mountain
programme.desc: Ming-dynastian aikaisessa Kiinassa eraan buddhalaistemppelin johtajan on aika nimittaa seuraajansa. Mutta ehdokkaiden joukossa on heita, joiden ensisijaisena tavoitteena on varastaa mittaamattoman arvokkaat pyhat kirjoitukset temppelin aarrekammiosta. Kun henkilokohtaiset tavoitteet ja hengelliset pyrkimykset tormaavat, tuloksena on juonittelua ja liittoutumia.

programme.title: Final Shot
programme.desc: Salamurhaaja Frank on jattanyt aiemman tyonsa ja yrittaa nyt elaa naennaisesti tavallista elamaa tyttoystavansa ja tyttarensa kanssa. Pahamaineinen mafiapomo tulee yhtena paivana kaymaan pyytaakseen Frankilta apua. Mafiapomon nuori tytar on surmattu. Frank ei halua vetaa perhettaan mukaan mahdollisiin ongelmiin, ja hanen on paatettava, tekeeko murhan pomonsa puolesta vai saako rauhan omalle sielulleen.

programme.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 3
programme.desc: Eletaan 1600-luvun alkua feodaaliajan Japanissa, ja ratsain kulkeva mies jaa vangiksi taistelussaan samurairyhmaa vastaan. Vajaat 400 vuotta myohemmin toimittaja April O’Neil hankkii kirpputorilta lahjoja kilpikonnaystavilleen. Tavarat ovat enimmakseen harmittomia, mutta Tikku-mentori saa vanhan japanilaisen valtikan. Valtikka katkee sisalleen taikavoimia, ja yhtakkia sankarimme loytavat itsensa samuraiden Japanista, jossa he paatyvat keskelle kilpailevien laaninherrojen sotaa.

programme.title: American Exit
programme.desc: Charlie Bond on tienhaarassa elamassaan. Han on eronnut hiljattain vaimostaan, kun hanta pyydetaan huolehtimaan viikonloppuna pojastaan Leosta. Huono ajoitus, silla Charlie on juuri toteuttamassa taidevarkautta helpon rahan toivossa. Leo ei tieda suunnitelmasta mitaan, han odottaa vain, etta saisi olla kaivatun isan kanssa. Samalla todellisuus saa Charlien kiinni; haikailemattomat ammattitappajat jahtaavat hanta. Hanen ainoa toivonsa on paeta maasta ja parantaa suhteensa Leoon, jota han on laiminlyonyt monet vuodet.

programme.title: Banaanipojat hula-hula saarella
programme.desc: Huoletonta elamaa viettava onnenonkija Alan saa kasiinsa aarrekartan, josta selviaa japanilaisten sotajoukkojen toisen maailmansodan aikana katkeman rahasaaliin sijainti. Rahojen loytaminen on kuitenkin helpommin sanottu kuin tehty. Aarre sijaitsee kaukaisella trooppisella autiosaarella ja lisaksi kartan perassa ovat kaupungin gangsterit.Paastakseen roistoja pakoon ja aarretta etsimaan, piiloutuu Alan rauhaa rakastavan Charlien veneeseen. Monen mutkan ja koitoksen jalkeen Alan ja Charlie paasevat saarelle, ainoastaan huomatakseen ettei se olekaan asumaton.

programme.title: Buddy villissa lannessa
programme.desc: Trinity –veli Bud Spencer jalleen vauhdissa Villissa Lannessa. Hujari Buddya luullaan laakariksi, kun hanen kaverinsa Cocoa varastaa vahingossa laukun taynna kirurgin valineita. Han asettuu pikkukaupungin laakariksi, joka kayttaa omaperaisia menetelmia. Kun hurjat rikolliset yrittavat vallata kultakaivoksen paalla sijaitsevan kaupungin, paasevat Buddyn todelliset kyvyt esiin. Han on mestari lyomaan turpaan saveltajaleganda Ennio Morriconen saveltaman musiikin tahtiin!

programme.title: Triassic Hunt
programme.desc: Kun kaksi geneettisesti kehiteltya dinosaurusta karkaa laboratoriosta, joukko palkkasotilaita kutsutaan ottamaan ne kiinni. Mutta kun sotilaat tajuavat, etta dinosaurukset ovat yhta viisaita kuin ihmiset, alkaa uskomaton kissa- ja hiirileikki.

programme.title: TMNT
programme.desc: Splinter; rotta sensei; aistii, etta hanen nelja teini-ikaista kilpikonnaopettajaansa ovat eronneet ja heidan on luotava side voittaakseen muinaisen hirvion.

programme.title: Impact Earth
programme.desc: Liity tahtitieteen professorin matkaan, kun han kilpailee aikaa vastaan ​​pelastaakseen perheensa maata kohti suuntautuvalta katastrofaaliselta asteroidilta yrittaen samalla varoittaa maailmaa. Selviytyyko ihmiskunta?

programme.title: Suoraa toimintaa (Missing in Action)
programme.desc: Amerikkalaiset sotilaat ovat vangittuina Vietnamissa — ja yhden miehen tehtavana on tuoda heidat kotiin tassa vauhdikkaassa toiminta/seikkailuelokuvassa, jossa paaosassa on kamppailulajien legenda Chuck Norris. Rohkean pako yrityksen jalkeen sotavankileirilta eversti James Braddock (Norris) on tehtavassa paikantaa ja pelastaa kadonneita sotilaita valtiovarainministerion virkamiehen (Lenore Kasdorf) ja entisen armeijakaverin (M. Emmet Walsh) avustuksella. Tama yhden miehen armeija on valmis tunkeutumaan Vietnamiin… mutta paaseeko han sielta takaisin?

programme.title: Godsend
programme.desc: Menetettyaan poikansa, Paul ja Jessie Duncan paattavat antaa salaperaisen laakarin kloonata poika. Asiat saavat pahaenteisen kaanteen pojan kasvaessa ja he saavat tietaa jarkyttavan salaisuuden laakarista.

programme.title: Once Upon a Time in China
programme.desc: Eletaan 1800-luvun loppua Kaakkois-Kiinassa, ja kung-fu-mestari Wong Fei Hun on ainoa, joka puolustaa kotiseutuaan miehittajavaltiolta, joka on jo ottanut haltuunsa Hongkongin ja Macaon. Samaan aikaan kun legendaarinen kansansankari Wong taistelee oman henkensa ja kansansa puolesta, orastaa romanssi vastustamattoman Siu-kwanin kanssa. Once Upon a Time in China on Jet Lin ensimmainen elokuva Wong Fei Hungin roolissa. Sita pidetaan yhtena Hongkong-elokuvien kultakauden parhaista elokuvista.

programme.title: Texas Red
programme.desc: Tositarina legendaarisesta Texas Redista, afroamerikkalaisesta miehesta, jota sadat laittomat cowboyt jahtasivat rajusti pitkin preerian karua maisemaa Mississippin talvisen eramaan halki. Kaikki halutuimman palkinnon saamiseksi.

programme.title: Reunalla
programme.desc: Uskallatko ottaa seuraavan askeleen? Vankikarkuri Nick Cassidy ilmestyy yhtakkia pilvenpiirtajan reunukselle New Yorkissa. Aikooko han hypata? Pian kaikkien tiedotusvalineiden ja koko kaupungin huomio kiinnittyy Nickiin. Ja kun kaikki katsovat ylospain, kukaan ei huomaa ovelaa ryostoa, joka tehdaan kadun toisella puolella. Liittyvatko tapaukset toisiinsa? Paaseeko poliisipsykologi Linda totuuden jaljille? Ja onko Nickilla oikeasti jokin aivan toinen suunnitelma?

programme.title: Turpiin vaan ja onnea
programme.desc: Tavanomaista Spencer - Hill -mattoa. Matt Kirby ja Wilbur Walsh (Hill and Spencer) ovat hieman aggressiivisia luonteita ja joutuvatkin usein vaikeuksiin, joista kuitenkin yleensa selviytyvat nyrkkiensa avulla. Eraana paivana he tormaavat toisiinsa ja paattavat suorittaa ryostokeikan. Mutta jonkun sekaannuksen takia he varvaytyvat vahingossa poliiseiksi. Turpiin vaan ja onnea! on tavanomainen Terence Hill – Bud Spencer -elokuva, eli luvassa on huumoria ja nyrkkitappeluja. Naille italialaisperaisille elokuville on myos tyypillista melko olematon juoni. Ei naita elokuvia ole tarkoitettukaan miksikaan muuksi kuin viikonlopun viihteeksi.

programme.title: The Fourth Musketeer
programme.desc: Nuori dArtagnan matkustaa isansa puolesta Gasconyn maaseudulta Pariisiin, jossa han on mukana kuninkaan muskettisoturien ja kardinaali Richelieun vartijoiden valisessa ovelassa ja erittain monimutkaisessa juonessa. Veri vuodatetaan, ja niiden, jotka eivat ole varuillaan, on asetettava henkensa vaaraan.

programme.title: Meidan gangstereiden kesken
programme.desc: Painija Charlie ja jaatelonmyyja Sonny ovat huolettomia ja mukavia kavereita, jotka pysyttelevat poissa vaikeuksista. Mutta kun kaupungin ja alamaailman johtaja erehtyy luulemaan heita pahamaineiseksi tappajakaksikoksi, kaikki muuttuu... Pelastaakseen omat nahkansa Charlie ja Sonny pysyvat vaiti todellisista henkilollisyyksistaan ja pelaavat mukana hamatakseen gangstereita. Kun Charlie ja Tom saavat tehtavakseen hoidella kilpaileva perhe paivilta, ei heille jaa muuta mahdollisuutta kuin ottaa ohjat omiin kasiinsa... Bud Spencerin ystavaa Sonnya nayttelee Giuliano Gemma. Han on muun muassa vaikuttanut spaghettiwesternelokuvassa ”Ringo - tappaja” ja Dario Argenton jannarissa ”Tenebre”.

programme.title: Instrument of War
programme.desc: Kun Yhdysvaltain ilmavoimien B-24 pommikoneen pilotti Clair Cline ammutaan alas ja vangitaan Saksassa, hanen osaltaan yksi sota loppuu ja toinen - toivon yllapitaminen - alkaa. Natsien piikkilanka-aitojen saartama Cline ja muut sotavangit etsivat selviamisen lisaksi keinoja peitota vankeus. Perustuu tositapahtumiin.

programme.title: Salt And Fire
programme.desc: Tutkija kidnapataan ja heitetaan tappavaan autiomaahan, jossa hanen on taisteltava luonnonvoimia vastaan selvitakseen.

programme.title: Banaanipojat hula-hula saarella
programme.desc: Huoletonta elamaa viettava onnenonkija Alan saa kasiinsa aarrekartan, josta selviaa japanilaisten sotajoukkojen toisen maailmansodan aikana katkeman rahasaaliin sijainti. Rahojen loytaminen on kuitenkin helpommin sanottu kuin tehty. Aarre sijaitsee kaukaisella trooppisella autiosaarella ja lisaksi kartan perassa ovat kaupungin gangsterit.Paastakseen roistoja pakoon ja aarretta etsimaan, piiloutuu Alan rauhaa rakastavan Charlien veneeseen. Monen mutkan ja koitoksen jalkeen Alan ja Charlie paasevat saarelle, ainoastaan huomatakseen ettei se olekaan asumaton.

programme.title: Spaghettiman
programme.desc: Clarkilla ei ole myotatuntoa millekaan eika kenellekaan. Han ei valita tippaakaan maailmasta, jossa me elamme, tuskin itsestaankaan. Mutta vanhan, spagettia taynna olevan kattilan ja rikkinaisen mikron kanssa sattuneen tapahtuman jalkeen jokin menee taysin pieleen. Clark muuttuu supersankariksi, joka voi taistella rikollisuutta vastaan spagetilla. Mutta siina on yksi koukku - hanelle pitaa maksaa.

programme.title: Banana Joe
programme.desc: Banaani Joen elama on yhta auringonpaistetta. Lokoisaa iloista oloa, ilman stressia etelaisella paratiisisaarella, kunnes... Joen asuinkyla on jaamassa modernin business-kulttuurin jalkoihin. Pian paikkaa pyorittavat byrokraatit ja jengit, pykalineen ja paheineen. Korruptio ja saantoviidakko alkavat rehottaa paratiisissa, ja huoleton vapauden aurinko on jaamassa pahasti pyrkyreiden ja rahastajien varjoon. Joe ei lainkaan pida siita mita on tapahtumassa, eika ole valmis luopumaan idyllisesta paratiisistaan ilman taistelua. On aika takoa nyrkein joidenkin paahan jarkea, ja nayttaa mista kuuluu ja kuka kaskee!

programme.title: Flight World War II
programme.desc: Nykyaikaisen 757:n matkustajat tekevat aikamatkan takaisin 1940-luvulle ja joutuvat kamppailemaan hengestaan keskella saksalaisten ja liittoutuneitten taistelua. Yrittaessaan pysya hengissa he onnistuvat vaikuttamaan historiaan ja toisen maailmansodan loppuratkaisuun.

programme.title: Street Fighter: The Legend Of Chun-Li
programme.desc: Erittain suosittuun videopeliin perustuva toimintaseikkailu on todella vauhdikas ja seksikas! Chun-Li saa selville, etta hanen isansa on kidnapattu, ja han joutuu sukeltamaan Hongkongin raakaan alamaailmaan. Han janoaa kostoa ja kohtaa lopulta kaikkien aikojen hurjimman verivihollisensa. Iskut ovat napakoita ja teraksenlujia - Street Fighter on taas taalla!

programme.title: Awake
programme.desc: Mies heraa sairaalassa, eika hanella ole muistikuvaa siita, kuka han on tai miten han paatyi sinne. Hanta hoitava Diana (Eastwood) ei loyda mitaan henkilopapereita, joten han kutsuu miesta John Doeksi (Rhys Meyers). Poliisi syyttaa Johnia sarjamurhaajaksi, joka on tappanut useita nuoria naisia alueella. Kun Johnia aiotaan kuulustella, han onnistuu pakenemaan Dianan avulla, joka on varma hanen syyttomyydestaan. He ajavat viimeisimmalle rikospaikalle etsimaan johtolankoja ja vastauksia todistaakseen Johnin syyttomyyden. Hyva sairaanhoitaja kuulee raastavan totuuden Johnin henkilollisyydesta seka valheiden ja petosten verkosta, joka vie Johnin viela viimeiseen ratkaisevaan taisteluun.

programme.title: Get the Gringo
programme.desc: Driverilla (Gibson) on ollut huono paiva, ja se huononee vain entisestaan. Hanen juuri tekemansa miljoonakeikan oli tarkoitus taata miehelle leppoisa kesaloma, mutta loistoidean toteutus menee pain etelaa – kirjaimellisesti. Kaahatessaan pakoon Yhdysvaltain rajavartijoilta verinen ruumis takapenkillaan, Driver hurauttaa vahingossa autonsa rajan lapi, kierahtaa rajusti ja pysahtyy… Meksikon puolella. Paikallisviranomaiset passittavat miehen maan pahamaineisimpaan ”El Puebliton” vankilaan, jonka lait ovat yhta oudot kuin vaarallisetkin.

programme.title: Teenage Mutant Ninja Turtles 3
programme.desc: Eletaan 1600-luvun alkua feodaaliajan Japanissa, ja ratsain kulkeva mies jaa vangiksi taistelussaan samurairyhmaa vastaan. Vajaat 400 vuotta myohemmin toimittaja April O’Neil hankkii kirpputorilta lahjoja kilpikonnaystavilleen. Tavarat ovat enimmakseen harmittomia, mutta Tikku-mentori saa vanhan japanilaisen valtikan. Valtikka katkee sisalleen taikavoimia, ja yhtakkia sankarimme loytavat itsensa samuraiden Japanista, jossa he paatyvat keskelle kilpailevien laaninherrojen sotaa.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S02 : E22 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Vezi and Deborah love the house they purchased last season in Stouffville, but they are ready to make the move to the big city. They enlist the help of Inez Kudryk to show them the best properties she can find in Toronto, and they are especially keen on the Beaches neighborhood. Vezi works in the music industry, so Inez lines up some special surprises to wow her clients!

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S02 : E23 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Laura and Steven are a young couple with an expanding family, and are ready to take the next steps in home ownership. They want a large plot of land for their young children to run around and enjoy nature, and a spacious home that reflects this new phase of their life. Steve Bailey is the man for the job, and with such great homes to choose from, Laura and Steve will be hard pressed to pick just one!

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S02 : E25 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Sofie Kehdi heads back to Belize to help husband and wife team Rachel and Ben size up some resort properties. Along with their investors, Rachel and Ben are looking to purchase a resort on the island of Ambergris Caye that will provide the most bang for their buck. Each with a big personality of their own, it becomes clear this couple is not going to see eye to eye on what they want. Luckily for them, Sofie is a pro at mediating conflicts when it comes to real estate.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S02 : E26 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Sofie Kehdi heads back to Belize to help husband and wife team Rachel and Ben size up some resort properties. Along with their investors, Rachel and Ben are looking to purchase a resort on the island of Ambergris Caye that will provide the most bang for their buck. Each with a big personality of their own, it becomes clear this couple is not going to see eye to eye on what they want. Luckily for them, Sofie is a pro at mediating conflicts when it comes to real estate.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E01 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Julie and James are looking for a new home to raise their two boys. James is in the tech industry and would love an energy efficient home. Julie has her own dance studio and cant wait to get back to work after giving birth to her second son. Eve and Shawn are the perfect team for the job, especially with Timberworxs cutting edge "Net-Zero" project.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E02 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Giulia and Scott have recently come into an inheritance and want the house of their dreams. Currently, they live in a modest bungalow in a busy neighbourhood but would prefer to live in a secluded house with a magnificent view. Ideally, Giulia also wants a house that has separate living quarters for her ageing parents.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E04 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Laura is on the hunt for a new home for long time clients Marino and Paula. The couple and their three kids would like a spacious house with a country feel to escape their hectic lifestyles. Due to Marinos busy schedule as a producer, he would prefer a house that is all-inclusive and turnkey. Their kids are very active want a pool and the option for horse stables. Lauras going to find them the perfect home.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E05 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Louise, Jason, and their two children have been living in Europe for the past 10 years, but now they would like to be closer to their family in Canada. Louise absolutely adores the European aesthetic; the sense of luxury conveyed by multi-peaked roof-lines, bay-shaped windows, and decorative stone. She wants a house that allows them the feeling of "living abroad" without leaving the country.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E06 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Diogo is a dedicated musician working on his new album. He has been debating between moving to Miami or staying in Canada. Toronto is closer to his family and where he feels at home with his music. Danielle will show him some spectacular properties in both cities and see what he decides.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E08 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Tomarra and Rob had just married and blended their two families. As a new family, they want to transition to a quiet neighbourhood away from the hustle and bustle of Toronto. Steve is up for the challenge. Rob is a writer and plans to work from home, while Tomarra is a naturopath who would love to have her own studio. Ultimately, they want to start cherishing the real things in life, and that is spending more time with their kids.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E09 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Darlene and Bruce are in the market for a new home and have enlisted Laura to help them out. Darlenes one request is that they stay close to their current home, where their daughter goes to school. For Bruce, quality construction materials and workmanship are of paramount importance. One thing the entire family agrees on is that the backyard should have a fantastic entertainment space since they spend plenty of time together outdoors and enjoy having guests over.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E10 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Kathryn and Neil are true urbanites. They love what downtown Toronto has to offer. When Neil found out his company was relocating to Guelph, they werent thrilled. After five months of long commutes, the Thompson family is ready to take the risk and make a move-with some conditions. The new house has to have a pool and playroom for the kids and a large entertainment area for adults. Eves challenge is to find them an enticing home that will convince their friends from the city to visit.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E11 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Ashley and Ali are ready to take their relationship and living situation to the next level. The young entrepreneurs are prepared to move into a house, but the one thing they cant agree on is where to live. Ashley wants an estate home outside the city that has an outdoor pool and beautifully manicured gardens. Ali, on the other hand, insists on being close to his downtown office and walking distance from restaurants and shops.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S03 : E13 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Steve Bailey, Mike Donia and Daryl King review their favourite homes. Steve takes us down memory lane to his 18th century farmhouse, and another home with a stunning infinity pool. Daryls listings range from King city to Caloden, with helicopter pads and sprawling backyards. Mike brings us back to his fabulous listings in Thailand. He shows us a home made entirely of Bamboo, and billion-dollar property.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S04 : E01 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: George is a retired basket ball player, and Mada is an international model. For a man over 7 feet tall, finding the perfect house might be a challenge. Danielle knows high ceilings come in all shapes and sizes, can she find a style theyll like? They also want a pool and a home theatre.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S04 : E02 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Suhail and Niki have busy schedules. Hes a marketing director and shes a doctor so shes often on call for a hospital downtown. Can they find a place that can help relieve stress, but also be close enough to downtown for those urgent calls? They want a secluded home with at least 1 acre and magnificent views.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S04 : E03 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Wendy and Daniel are looking to downsize after their kids have moved out, but still want an elegant home. Shes a physical therapist and shes a business analyst. They want something that can help them relax at the end of the day, with at least 4 bedrooms and away from the downtown core. Can Lou find them something that fits?

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S04 : E05 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Janelle and Manuel are young professionals looking for more space. With one child tagging along on the tour already, they need a place for their growing family. They might need to do some renovations, but they want everything to be perfect.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S04 : E06 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: These two business owners Joseph and Heather work hard and want to play hard! Theyre looking for a place to entertain guests, and Daryls got some amazing homes to show them.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S05 : E01 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Vipins family of four are in the market to purchase their own dream home in the Greater Toronto Area.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S05 : E03 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Elvira and Robert are looking for a home with a history, but want to make sure it is post-renovation.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent

programme.desc: When Dana and Eric arent busy with their successful family business, they have their hands full with their 4 children.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent

programme.desc: Jonathan and Kerry are in the market for a new home to share memories in with their family; with a budget of 12 million dollars, Real Estate Agent Tav Schembri is challenged to find the family their dream home.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent

programme.desc: Nathan, a start up company owner and his fiance Kelsey, a owner of a holistic nutrition company, are open to purchasing a house anywhere in the GTA.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent

programme.desc: Katerina and Mauricio are looking for one property in Canada and a holiday home in Belize, specifically on a private island.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent

programme.desc: Fernando and his investment group are looking to either buy or build a resort in Canada or Mexico with the help of Joe Petrella Construction.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent

programme.desc: Real Estate Agents Jasmine Xuereb and Laura Compagni team up to aid power couple Jamie and Jennifer in purchasing either a real estate investment in Canada or Belize.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S06 : E05 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: The brokers explore Central America to find real estate options that fit the bill for two buyers looking for a change of scene.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S07 : E01 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Mike team up once again with local agent to find a unique opportunities for residential investments.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S07 : E02 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Marshall and Maria cant decide whether they should buy a property in Canada (Marshalls homeland) or Cuba (Marias homeland).

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent

programme.desc: Mike Donia locates an ultra-luxurious, private paradise for two buyers on Pearl Island, Panama, boasting 30 km of coastline and a rich marine sanctuary.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent

programme.desc: Tav and Mike team up once again to find unique opportunities in Canada as well villas in Los Cabos, Mexico.

programme.desc: Laura Compagni teams up with Mataj Architects and The Parentela Family to introduce the first of the Hotel Vie chain of luxury hotels.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Downsizing can be a difficult transition and Jins objective is to make it as seamless as possible. In this episode, Jin is getting outdoors by practicing archery with Mike but mostly just to compete for bragging rights. Jins client is moving from a house in Port Credit to a luxurious condo close to the downtown core. They desire extra bedrooms for when their children are visiting, all the amenities, and waterfront views.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E03 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Mikes couple is looking for their luxurious dream home anywhere in between Toronto and Barrie near HWY 400 in a prestigious neighborhood. They have a large dog, tall family, and want to start a family of their own. This means they are going to need a lot of space and want the house to be fully renovated or brand-new. Mike is the perfect agent for this couple because he lives, eats, and breathes the luxury lifestyle.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E04 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: An amazing beachfront property is what Inezs couple is looking for and these top million dollar agents are sure to surpass their expectations. Inezs client currently lives in a condo and have one child, however, they desire a home that they can comfortably expand their family in.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E05 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Mikes friend invites him to an Indian wedding and tells him about his uncle who is looking for a luxury condo close to the airport. Daryl, Inez, and Jin support and donate to Mikes charity after winning a bet amongst them and the amount is determined by how long Mike lasts in the ring boxing against a professional. This client is looking for an investment property and a place for him to live when visiting.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E06 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Somewhere to spend the rest of their days surrounded by nature sounds like a paradise to retire in. Daryl and Jin play some golf to discuss a potential listing she has found and Mike aids Inez in purchasing a new vehicle. Daryls client has older children with their own families now so they are looking for a home with lots of land and nature. It is very important to them because they want to be able to have everyone comfortably visit and eventually retire here in a few years.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E08 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Moving in together can be stressful but fun because you are starting a new life together! Inezs client is selling their separate properties and looking for a house or condo in the city or beach area that is close to shopping, groceries, schools, etc. Inezs couple is not too picky and open to different kinds of properties. Daryl and Inez enjoy a beautiful bike ride along the beaches boardwalk to discuss her client and the perfect luxury listing he has found.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E09 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Agreeing on a vacation home is made much harder when these top million dollar agents have astounding listings. Mikes client is looking for a waterfront cottage with lots of land and privacy. What better way to check out some waterfront listings then from a helicopter? Debbie wants a family cottage that feels homey, however, Paul wants an impressive high-end cottage that he can bring his business clients to.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E10 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Remarrying is hard enough let alone combining two families under one roof. With a total of 4 children between the ages of 7 and 16 Jins client is definitely going to need lots of space and land in a safe neighborhood. Daryl, Inez, and Mike attend Jins band practice to support her and listen to the set list they have prepared for an upcoming charity event. Jin gets her nails done frequently and this time Daryl decides to join her for some much needed pampering.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E11 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Now that Kristen and Kane have opened an office in Toronto, they will be travelling a lot from Vancouver and want somewhere of their own to stay in. Daryl and the other top million dollar agents have a wide range to search over because Daryls client is willing to live an hour or two drive away from downtown Toronto. Daryl, Jin, and Mike meet up for lunch in Port Dover to discuss business and later in the episode Mike and Daryl get their hands dirty in the kitchen at Sababa Restaurant.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S01 : E13 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Deborah and Vezi are an international couple that want to live in Toronto for one year but has no idea where to start looking. Luckily for them Mike, Jin, Daryl, and Inez have teamed up to find them the home of their dreams. They agree to split the commission and throw a yacht party for the clients decision. Mike arranges a private plane for all four agents to go to Montreal and discuss in style what the client is looking for.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S02 : E02 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Will Daryl be able to dazzle his clients and find a property that will take their breath away? This episode features the first two of four properties, with a special guest appearance by Design Generation builder and designer Carlo Rinomato.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S02 : E10 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: With the help of local realtor Daniel Hartin, Sofie sets her sights on the perfect home...and hopefully a bit of fun in the sun! This episode features the last two of four properties, as well as the reveal of which house the client decides to purchase.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent

programme.desc: Jessica and Mark are a young couple living and working in Thailand after meeting there several years ago and falling in love. They are looking for a permanent home in Bangkok, and after chatting with her friend Mae, Jessica knows that Mike Donia is the man for the job.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S02 : E13 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: After helping them find a home last season, Inez is enlisted by Martin and Cheryl to help them find the perfect investment property. While Cheryl wants a property with minimal work and no landlord responsibilities, Martin is more open to renovations and taking on some of the commonplace duties associated with property management.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S02 : E14 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: This episode features the last two of four properties, as well as the reveal of which house the clients decide to purchase, with special guest appearances by interior design expert Shelley Alexanian and guest agent Mo Loulou.

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent

programme.desc: This weeks episode features Cambridge realtor extraordinaire Steve Bailey as he helps couple Dan and Melinda search for the perfect home. Its a real battle of contemporary vs. traditional as Dan and Melinda hash it out over where their future lies. Melinda surprises Dan with some new information, but can Steve surprise them both by showing them the perfect property?

programme.title: Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.sub-title: S02 : E17 Top Million Dollar Agent
programme.desc: Vancouver-based couple Jim and Shannon are looking to relocate to their hometown of Toronto with their two daughters. With a budget of 10 million dollars, they enlist the help of savvy realtor Sofie Kehdi. While it might first seem that Jim and Shannon are on the same page, the house hunt proves that they have some differing opinions on what makes a good investment.

programme.title: Japan: Mass consumption - What the labels forget to mention - Part 2
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Earth from above - Season 3 - Japan: Mass consumption - What the labels forget to mention - Part 2
programme.desc: Above all, these reports are an opportunity for Yann Arthus-Bertrand to take stock of the planet and denounce certain human behaviors that are at the root of dramatic, even irreversible, environmental and climatic degradation. Off to Tokyo, then Kenya, to an animal sanctuary. Then on to Mount Fuji to learn how to live there, and all the plastic that clogs up the seas. Reports will focus on everyday products, chosen for their destructive production practices for both people and the environment.

programme.title: The taste of bread
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Julies Frenchy Cookbook - Season 4 - The taste of bread
programme.desc: Today, Julie takes you on a bread trail to uncover the dedicated artisan bakers and millers. Her adventure will lead her through the Libourne region, then onwards to the North of France, the Ardèche, and the Aisne, where bakers have transformed bread into a powerful catalyst for social cohesion. While some individuals may avoid bread, particularly due to gluten-related concerns, others have chosen to reposition it at the forefront of the dining experience by championing its nutritional benefits. This commitment is shared by several chefs whom Julie will meet at the conclusion of her expedition.

programme.title: Juliette (Morbihan)
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Juliette (Morbihan)
programme.desc: Juliette has long been aware of the delicate beauty of nature. For years she spent her life on the sea, organising regattas for the traditional sailboats that are famous in the French region of Morbihan. Her appreciation for the elements made for a smooth transition as she decided to leave the water behind and return to the earth. Learning to shape a ball of clay into a graceful and elegant object, she discovered a passion for ceramics. Today, she lives from her creations and makes pieces that reflect their surroundings, the stunning Gulf of Morbihan.

programme.title: Anna (Brittany)
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Anna (Brittany)
programme.desc: Anna’s unusual background provided inspiration for her life change. Her career began as a wolf trainer for cinema and it was during these years that she developed her deep love for animals. After being tired of seeing them used as props and constantly in cages, she decided to leave the world of show business behind and start an eco-friendly sheep and goat pasture. To further share her passion for these gentle animals, Anna has opened a conservatory farm where visitors can experience first-hand the joys of being close to nature. She also makes amazing goat cheese!

programme.title: Cristina (Spain)
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Cristina (Spain)
programme.desc: At 31 years old, the last thing Cristina expected when she went to see the doctor about a blocked ear was to leave the consultation with a diagnosis for Breast Cancer. This young and passionate sociologist decided to apply the same philosophy to her treatment as she did when surfing: when a wave crashes down on you, get up and try again. Through her healing journey she deepened her love for the ocean and also discovered the therapeutic capabilities of yoga for cancer patients. Today she shares her practice through surf and yoga retreats and is specialised in oncological yoga, helping others heal.

programme.title: Idoia (Spain)
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 My Zen People - Season 4 - Idoia (Spain)
programme.desc: Idoia thrives on weaving together the sources of inspiration that surround her. Heavily influenced by the natural beauty of her home region of Galicia, Spain, she creates unique woven pieces from diverse and beautiful materials. Idoia’s pieces represent her vision of a modern woman, drawing from the traditions and experiences of those who perfected the craft before her and also pushing to innovate and adapt her creations for the modern world. Her recent collaboration with luxury fashion house Loewe is a dream come true for this modern artisan.

programme.title: Nature’s Heroes: Bangladesh - Part 1
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Earth from above - Season 4 - Nature’s Heroes: Bangladesh - Part 1
programme.desc: With Bangladesh as a running thread, Yann Arthus-Bertrand meets several people who have changed their lives to dedicate themselves to a major project. In Bangladesh, Yves and Runa Marre have created the Friendship Foundation. Among other things, they’ve created a floating hospital installed on an old barge bought in France. Julie Andersen, an ex-advertising executive from New York has come to South Africa to defend sharks with her Shark Angels Foundation. In North India, Kartik Satyanarayan is helping to stop the dreadful exploitation of the lippus bears (dancing bears). He’s created Wildlife SOS, a preserve to rehabilitate the bears that have been rescued and to give work to the men of...

programme.title: USA: The end of oil - Part 1
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Earth from above - Season 3 - USA: The end of oil - Part 1
programme.desc: "The end of oil" is the amazing story of a raw material which has revolutionized mans life in just a century. But today, oil reserves are depleting. In his crazy race for always more production, Man didnt manage to preserve this precious energy that took million years for the Earth to give out. To tell the adventure of oil, Yann Arthus-Bertrand and his team went to the United States, the country which depends the most on black gold. At the start of the 21st century, it is now urgent to realize that oil resources are limited. Its today that we have to act and get organized, in order to prepare the new era to come. While all our economies are based on the petrol barrels price, well...

programme.title: A la carte grills
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Julies Frenchy Cookbook - Season 4 - A la carte grills
programme.desc: If youre a nature enthusiast and a fan of outdoor cooking, the upcoming season is perfect for barbecue enthusiasts! Our journey will take us to Aube, nestled in the heart of the Brevonnes forest, and then to the Massif des Bauges, where grilling and snow create a unique combination. Afterward, well explore the Libournais region, where well uncover cooking techniques that make use of vine shoots, which are plentiful in the area. Just a short distance from the vineyards, well arrive at another corner of Gironde, the Blaye region, where the cooking method remains consistent but features a distinctly local ingredient: eel.

programme.title: The flavors of flowers
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Julies Frenchy Cookbook - Season 4 - The flavors of flowers
programme.desc: Eating flowers might appear unconventional, but we often consume them without even realizing it. Consider artichokes, for instance : they are essentially large, unopened flowers. Capers are the preserved buds of flowers soaked in vinegar, and cloves are dried flower buds. We also find courgette flowers, saffron pistils, orange blossom water used to flavor pastries, and the violet sweets that evoke memories of our childhood. In addition to adding aesthetic appeal and providing a dose of vitamins to our plates, flowers elevate the flavors of a dish and can even serve as a vegetable substitute.

programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 The Blue Zones of Longevity - Season 1 - Destination Okinawa
programme.desc: Genetic, biological, cultural and dietary factors combine to make the Japanese island of Okinawa a zone of extreme longevity. Why is it that cancer is virtually non-existent here? Well see that the famous Japanese trio of "rice, fish and soy" is not the key to longevity, but a diet based on plants, lots of green leafy vegetables and endemic sweet potatoes. Self-restriction and strong social ties are other elements that our naturopathic chef and attending physician will discover on site, together with local inhabitants and scientists.

programme.title: USA: The end of oil - Part 2
programme.sub-title: S01 : E01 Earth from above - Season 3 - USA: The end of oil - Part 2
programme.desc: "The end of oil" is the amazing story of a raw material which has revolutionized mans life in just a century. But today, oil reserves are depleting. In his crazy race for always more production, Man didnt manage to preserve this precious energy that took million years for the Earth to give out. To tell the adventure of oil, Yann Arthus-Bertrand and his team went to the United States, the country which depends the most on black gold. At the start of the 21st century, it is now urgent to realize that oil resources are limited. Its today that we have to act and get organized, in order to prepare the new era to come. While all our economies are based on the petrol barrels price, well...

programme.desc: In 2003, Masashi Hirao became the last apprentice of Japans great Bonsai master Saburo Kato. Before Saburo-san died he passed on to his apprentice a seemingly impossible mission: to prevent the 1000 year old art from dying-out in the face of a rapidly changing world and achieve his master’s vision of bringing peace to the world through bonsai. Masashi’s early efforts are dogged by many failures but combining his master’s guidance and modern instincts he sets out to travel the world and discover the way, drawing on innovative trends in contemporary art.
